lead_paragraph: Belgian Tom Boonen of the Etiix-Quick Step team won the 202-km RideLondon-Surrey Classic in a dramatic sprint finish on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Boonen Wins RideLondon Classic in Sprint Finish
